Revision history for PostgreSQL extension pg_idx_advisor.

0.1.1  2015-06-17 21:00:00
      - BugFix: Statistics can now exist on the tables.
      - BugFix: memory leaks.
      - Initial work to comply with PG 9.5

0.1.0  2015-05-27 11:47:43
      - Initial version.
      - Implementation in C.
      - Included in [PGXN Manager](https://github.com/theory/pgxn-manager).
      - Not otherwise released.
